{
  "texts": [
    "Search queries were developed based on these identified research areas.",
    "For each area, three types of queries were formulated: a broad query for comprehensive scope, a focused query using the \"+\" operator for higher specificity, and a related query incorporating alternative or supplementary terms using the \"|\" operator.",
    "This multi-search strategy, executed within Semantic Scholar as previously detailed, was designed to balance the retrieval of a broad scope of relevant studies with the precise identification of highly relevant results.",
    "Table 1 presents the complete set of search queries.",
    "Search topics and query strategies for the systematic review."
  ]
}